    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EARLY ACCESS DISCLAIMER</h2><br>- There is Currently 1 to 2 hours worth of content if you unlock everything.<br>- There will be bugs, i'm a solo Developer and i'm releasing content rapidly. So i don't get a chance to play the game every time i update it.<br>- If you join the Early Access be ready to report bugs, i am full time, so if you report it to my discord and get my attention i can fix it the same day.<br><br>- You guys are super important to the future of Freedom Drive. Leave suggestions, i am more then willing to listen.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/147d84e8438c21da7b9d754349b5e316.avif?t=1697324640\" width=215 height=88 /></span><br><br>Defeat the Boss of each location. Survive the Onslaught of deadly vehicles, environments. <br>Unlock new, faster, stronger or stranger vehicles to aid you in your mission for Freedom. Build your strength to take on stronger challengers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/9ee6d90972cde2608edc76aea87ffe71.apng?t=1697324640\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/9ee6d90972cde2608edc76aea87ffe71.poster.avif?t=1697324640\" class=\"bb_img\" width=400 height=114 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrades</h2>Mountains of weapons to customize your play style. You can use  Heavy Flamers to melt away problems, or Flying Saw Blades that travel a great distance and hit multiple enemies at once!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/a2e1ddd66e5794ba8764190b9290dd8b.poster.avif?t=1697324640\" width=460 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/a2e1ddd66e5794ba8764190b9290dd8b.webm?t=1697324640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicles</h2>There is a vehicle for every play style. From speed Demons, to slow lumbering impenetrable goliaths. Each vehicle comes with its own main weapon and upgrades to diversify the playing field.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/56c443be2495e6e3b9ddf9c8887b3e26.poster.avif?t=1697324640\" width=428 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/56c443be2495e6e3b9ddf9c8887b3e26.webm?t=1697324640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maps</h2>Three biomes with three maps each full of new enemies to challenge your freedom. Each map is home to a unique boss and environmental hazards for you to learn and take advantage of - or die trying.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158510/extras/ee4092e890cac30cb4619d5727946a96.webp?t=1697324640\" width=44 height=47 /></span><br><br>-Early Access-<br>Find out everything you need to know on the discord <br><br>More information about the early access will become available closer to Early Access Release",
